assets.description:
#MASTERCOPY of Bolivian Artist Mamani Mamani's Pachamama painting 

Some behind-the-scenes notes:
‚Ä¢ I created the behind part of this painting out of the designs and characters that exist in the painting, see all around!

‚Ä¢ I met this amazing Bolivian artist, plus did some research and had an interview about his thoughts in life prior to the VR painting to get a better sense of how Mamani Mamani thinks of his art to try to imagine how he might have painted this in VR.

‚Ä¢ Mamani Mamani uses a lot of details in his art because of the deep understanding he has of Bolivian culture. 

‚Ä¢ To create his very recognizable fading of colors through the piece I used a mix of more than 3 brushed and took a LOT of time and effort, but the results are remarkable!

‚Ä¢ I loved using so many colors and brushes, also taking the time to imagine the painting as an sculpture. 

Hope you like it! If you want to learn more about Bolivian Artist Mamani Mamani head to http://mamanimamani-bolivia.blogspot.com/

To see more of my work https://www.adrianalaboliviana.com/
or my Poly profile

#galacticsafari
The Sentinel Army of The Empire Fsk.
Militant and merciless, any uninvited guests wandering foolishly into the barren waste of Tungath should expect to be met with extreme force by the Sentinel Army of The Empire Fsk. Armor plated and incredibly powerful, they have no need for weaponry. Numbered in the billions they mostly live below the surface of the planet in underground citadels but will quickly emerge en masse whenever their territory is violated.
